武汉已从阻击战转为反击战。
Wuhan has changed from a blockage to a counter-attack.
欧洲疫情迅速蔓延，单日新增近千2020年2月26日，在马来西亚雪邦，从武汉撤回的马籍民众抵达当地机场机场。
Epidemic spread rapidly across Europe, with nearly a thousand new arrivals a day on Feb. 26, 2020, in the Malaysian state of Cherbang, Malaysia, after horses were withdrawn from Wuhan.
图/ 法新文 |《财经》数据研究员徐进 图 |《财经》视觉中心 编辑 | 郝洲一、武汉战疫在新平台继续拉锯，国内再现输入病例今日国内简述：国内3月4日报告累计病例80409例，新增139例，低于意大利、伊朗、韩国等国。
Caijing data researcher Xu Jintu & # 44; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & nbsp; & nbsp; & nbsp; & nbsp; & nbsp; & nbsp; & nbsp; & nbsp; & nbsp; & nbsp; & nbsp; & nbsp;
新增病例131例来自武汉，广大非武汉地区仅8例，其中浙江的2例为境外（意大利）输入。
There were 131 new cases from Wuhan and only 8 cases from non-Wuhan areas, including 2 cases from Zhejiang province.
武汉仍保持在三位数，新增疑似病例61例，已经连续5天保持在两位数水平。
Wuhan, which remains in three digits with 61 new suspected cases, has remained at double-digit levels for five consecutive days.
中央指导组指出，武汉保卫战已从阻击战转为反击战、歼灭战。
The Central Steering Group pointed out that the defense of Wuhan had changed from a war of resistance to one of combat and annihilation.
全国人民都在期待武汉决胜时刻到来。
The whole country is looking forward to Wuhan decisive moment.
昨日召开的中央政治局常委会要求“加快建立同疫情防控相适应的经济社会运行秩序”，“力争全国经济社会发展早日全面步入正常轨道”，部署七项重要任务11次提到复工复产。
Yesterday's meeting of the Standing Committee of the Politburo called for "speeding up the establishment of an economic and social order suited to the prevention and control of the epidemic," and "striving to put the country's economic and social development on an early and full track."
证监会以视频审核方式召开鼠年首届发审会，融资功能恢复。
The Securities and Futures Commission held the first review meeting of the Year of the Rat via video audit.
上证指数重新站上3000点。
The Shanghai index is back on the 3000.
二、印度首现两位数增长，疫情已蔓延至79国（不含中国）图1欧洲又有三国首次确诊感染病例，可能很快欧洲将无一国家能独善其身。
Two, India's first double-digit growth, the epidemic has spread to 79 countries (excluding China) Figure 1 Three more cases of infection have been confirmed in Europe for the first time, and it is likely that soon no country in Europe will be left alone.
印度首次出现两位数增长，主要原因是一个来自意大利的旅行团出现多例确诊，这个旅行团的印度司机后来也被证实感染。
India's first double-digit growth was mainly due to a number of confirmed cases of a tour group from Italy whose Indian driver was later confirmed to be infected.
图2在中国以外，疫情扩散仍然集中在西太平洋（韩国）、欧洲（意大利、德国、法国和西班牙）和东地中海地区（伊朗），欧洲迎来大暴发的一天。
Figure 2 Outside China, the spread of the epidemic remains concentrated in the Western Pacific (South Korea), Europe (Italy, Germany, France and Spain) and the Eastern Mediterranean (Iran), ushering in a major outbreak in Europe.
随着美国确诊数字的增加，美洲地区的增长也有抬头之势。
Growth in the Americas is also on the rise as the number of confirmed cases in the United States increases.
图3小编担心这张图可能很快要扩员了。
FIG. 3 The editor worries that the map may soon be enlarged.
三、中韩之间的航班进一步缩减图4韩国防疫部门对“新天地”教会有新冠病毒肺炎症状的信徒进行的电询进入尾声。
Flights Between China and South Korea Further Shrinking Flights Figure 4 The Korean epidemic prevention agency is nearing the end of a televised inquiry into the New World Church's adherents of the new crown virus pneumonia.
专家表示，除“新天地”教会外，也应警惕其它地区社区感染。
Experts said that in addition to "Xintiandi" Church, but also should be alert to other areas of community infection.
截至目前，38个国家和地区对韩国采取全面或限期禁止入境措施，22个国家和地区对从韩国入境者进行隔离，34个国家和地区加大了来自韩国入境者的检疫力度。
So far, 38 countries and regions have adopted comprehensive or time-bound measures against entry into the ROK, 22 countries and regions have isolated people from the ROK, and 34 countries and regions have stepped up quarantine efforts for those from the ROK.
中国已有不少于15个省市，对来自韩国入境人员采取隔离措施。
No fewer than 15 provinces and cities in China have taken measures to segregate people from the Republic of Korea.
中外航空公司根据市场需求和疫情形势，减少了部分航班。
Domestic and foreign airlines have reduced some flights according to the market demand and epidemic situation.
本周中韩间的航班总量已降至320班，预计下周将进一步减至每周276班。
The total number of flights between the two Koreas dropped to 320 this week and is expected to drop further to 276 next week.
四、疫情在欧洲全面暴发图5由于英国、德国、法国、西班牙、瑞士、挪威、瑞典等国的确诊病例数激增，欧洲单日新增近1000例，由此可判断新冠疫情已经在欧洲全面暴发。
Fig. 5 A full-blown outbreak in Europe can be gauged from the surge in confirmed cases in the UK, Germany, France, Spain, Switzerland, Norway, Sweden, and nearly 1,000 new cases a day in Europe.
意大利国家卫生研究所传染病部门负责人乔瓦尼·雷扎说，预计未来几天确诊病例数还会以较高速度增长。
Giovanni Reza, director of infectious diseases at the National Institutes of Health in Italy, said the number of confirmed cases is expected to grow at a higher rate in the coming days.
【特别说明：以上统计，2月28日前为世卫组织官方统计数据，数据截止时间为北京时间每日17时；从2月28日开始，数据由《财经》根据公开资料统计，截止时间为北京时间每日9时】五、美国各州已做好测试准备图6新冠病毒在美国已经出现社区传播，但仍处于早期阶段。
Statistics above show that before Feb. 28, official WHO statistics are due at 17: 00 daily Beijing time. Since Feb. 28, the data have been compiled by Caijing at 9: 00 pm daily according to open data.
加利福尼亚州出现首例死亡。
The first death occurred in California.
美国副总统彭斯（Mike Pence）3月4日在记者会上宣布：“目前全部州立实验室及州立大学实验室已经准备好，进行新冠肺炎测试。
"All the state and state university labs are ready for the New Crown Pneumonia test," Vice President Mike Pence told a news conference on Monday.
无需联邦政府额外增援设备或资源。
No additional federal equipment or resources are required.
经美国食品及药物管理局（FDA）验证，他们已具备资质在各州和地方进行测试。
Verified by the United States Food and Drug Administration (FDA), they are qualified to conduct state and local tests.
”本周美国全国将发出约150万支（核酸）测试剂。
About 1.5 million nucleic acid (Nucleic Acid) testing agents will be sent out across the country this week.
六、全球疫情数字速览1、【日检量14000份】武汉移动P3实验室每天上午采集样本，下午1点进行检测，晚上11点前医生就能拿到每位患者的检测报告，一天可做600份核酸检测。
Wuhan Mobile P3 Laboratory takes samples every morning, tests them at 1 p.m., gets test reports from each patient by 11 p.m. and takes 600 nucleic acid tests a day.
除了3套移动P3实验室外，目前武汉市有40家核酸检测机构同时开工，日均检测量可以达到14000份左右，实现了目前武汉核酸检测日清日结。
In addition to three mobile P3 labs, 40 nucleic acid testing facilities in Wuhan have started at the same time, with an average daily detection of about 14,000, thus realizing the current Wuhan Nucleic Acid Detection Day.
2、【又1艘邮轮】据美国媒体报道，原定于当地时间3月4日晚抵达旧金山的“大公主号”邮轮已推迟时间，该邮轮上有11名乘客和10名船员出现感染新冠病毒的症状。
According to US media reports, the ship Princess, which was due to arrive in San Francisco on the night of March 4, was delayed with 11 passengers and 10 crew members showing signs of New Crown Virus infection.
该游轮上载有约2500名乘客，其中超过50%是加利福尼亚人。
The ship carried around 2,500 passengers, more than 50 per cent of whom were Californians.
3、【83亿美元抗疫预算】当地时间3月4日，美国国会众议院高票通过一项总金额为83亿美元的应对新冠病毒财政预算，预计国会参议院将在当地时间3月5日审议通过预算后报总统特朗普签字确认。
3, 2007-9-24 16: 23 [hide] "The House of Representatives voted overwhelmingly to approve a $8.3 billion budget for the New Crown virus, which is expected to be approved by the Senate on March 5 for confirmation by President Trump.
4、【840万学生停课】当地时间3月4日，意大利教育部长阿佐利纳宣布，新冠疫情发展迅速，决定自5日起关闭全国所有学校直至3月15日。
4, 8.4 million students suspended classes March 4, Italy's education minister announced that the new crown outbreak of rapid development, from 5 to close all schools throughout the country until March 15.
约840万学生将受到影响。
Some 8.4 million students will be affected.
此前，只有疫情的部分学校关闭。
Previously, only parts of the schools affected by the outbreak were closed.
5、【缺2600万只口罩】伊朗食品药品组织表示，每周全国需要4千万个口罩，目前正在试图进口N95口罩。
Iran's Food and Drug Organization says it needs 40 million face masks nationwide each week and is trying to import N95 masks.
据了解，目前伊朗口罩周产约1400万个，每周口罩缺口达2600万只。
It is understood that about 14 million Iranian masks around the week, a weekly gap of 26 million masks.
小结：武汉保卫战已从阻击战转为反击战、歼灭战。
Summary: The defense of Wuhan has changed from a defensive war to a war of annihilation and annihilation.
全国人民都在期待武汉决胜时刻到来。
The whole country is looking forward to Wuhan decisive moment.
欧洲的疫情迅速蔓延，单日新增几近破千。
The epidemic in Europe spread rapidly, with nearly a thousand new cases a day.
